2008年戴维斯於改編自[[百老汇|百老汇]]剧目的電影《[[聖訴|聖訴]]》中饰演穆勒太太一角，与[[梅丽·史翠普|梅丽·史翠普]]、[[菲臘·西摩·荷夫曼|菲臘·西摩·荷夫曼]]以及[[艾美·亚当斯|艾美·亚当斯]]同台飚戏。尽管戏份极少，<ref>{{cite news|last1=Caro|first1=Mark|title=Viola Davis: The Pop Machine interview|url=http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_popmachine/2009/02/viola-davis-the-pop-machine-interview.html|accessdate=2015-09-21|work=[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]|date=2009-02-14|archive-date=2015-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018092823/http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_popmachine/2009/02/viola-davis-the-pop-machine-interview.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 但她於劇中的表現却大受好评，並入圍了多項大奖，包括[[奥斯卡最佳女配角獎|奥斯卡最佳女配角獎]]与[[金球奖最佳電影女配角|金球奖最佳電影女配角]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/oscars/4315738/Oscar-nominations-2009-Amy-Adams-and-Viola-Davis-discuss-their-roles-in-Doubt.html|title=Oscar nominations 2009: Amy Adams and Viola Davis discuss their roles in Doubt|work=[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]|date=2009-01-22|accessdate=2012-07-08|archive-date=2015-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103110727/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/oscars/4315738/Oscar-nominations-2009-Amy-Adams-and-Viola-Davis-discuss-their-roles-in-Doubt.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2009年6月30日，戴維斯正式成為[[美国电影艺术与科学学会|美国电影艺术与科学学会]]正式会员。<ref>{{cite web|title=Academy Invites 134 to Membership|url=http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2009/20090630.html|work=oscars.org|date=2009-06-30|accessdate=2012-07-08|archive-date=2012-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120518164859/http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2009/20090630.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2010年6月13日，戴维斯凭借在奥格斯特·威斯尔新编话剧《{{link-en|藩籬 (話劇)|Fences (play)|藩籬}}》中对萝丝·麦克森的出色诠释，获得[[第64届托尼奖颁奖典礼|第64届東尼奖]]最佳女主角獎，<ref>{{cite web|title=Fences Stars Viola Davis & Denzel Washington Win 2010 Tony Awards|url=http://www.broadway.com/buzz/152732/fences-stars-viola-davis-denzel-washington-win-2010-tony-awards/|work=broadway.com|date=2010-06-13|accessdate=2012-07-08|archive-date=2013-07-16|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6IA1c1NRv?url=http://www.broadway.com/buzz/152732/fences-stars-viola-davis-denzel-washington-win-2010-tony-awards/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 使其成为繼[[菲麗西亞·拉沙德|菲麗西亞·拉沙德]]後，第二个获得该奖项的非裔美国女演员。

2011年8月，戴維斯在根据[[凱瑟琳·史托基特|凱瑟琳·史托基特]]{{link-en|姊妹 (小說)|The Help|同名小说}}改编的電影《[[相助|寫出友共鳴]]》中飾演愛比琳·克拉克，該劇獲得廣大的好評，而戴维斯的演技更是備受肯定，不僅獲[[奥斯卡金像獎|奥斯卡金像獎]]、<ref>Eggertsen, Chris (September 14, 2014). [http://www.hitfix.com/news/shocker-oscar-nominee-viola-davis-is-routinely-offered-mammy-ish-roles-by-hollywood "Shocker: Oscar nominee Viola Davis is routinely offered 'mammy-ish' roles by Hollywood"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hitfix.com/news/shocker-oscar-nominee-viola-davis-is-routinely-offered-mammy-ish-roles-by-hollywood |date=20150128132936 }}. [[HitFix|HitFix]].</ref> [[金球奖|金球奖]]和[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]最佳女主角獎提名，亦奪下多个影评人大奖以及[[美国演员工会奖|美国演员工会奖]][[美国演员工会奖最佳女主角|最佳女主角獎]]。

2012年，〈[[時代_(雜誌)|時代雜誌]]〉将维奥拉·戴维斯列为[[時代百大人物|時代百大人物]]之一。<ref name="Time 100"/> 同年，〈{{link-en|Glamour (雜誌)|Glamour (magazine)|Glamour}}〉將戴維斯命為Glamour年度電影女演員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.glamourmagazine.co.uk/celebrity/glamour-awards/winners-2012/film-actress-viola-davis|title=Film Actress – Viola Davis|work={{link-en|Glamour (雜誌)|Glamour (magazine)|Glamour}}|date=2012-05-29|accessdate=2012-07-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120621075034/http://www.glamourmagazine.co.uk/celebrity/glamour-awards/winners-2012/film-actress-viola-davis|archivedate=2012-06-21}}</ref> 6月12日，戴維斯從朋友兼同年奧斯卡競爭對手的梅麗·史翠普手中，獲頒{{link-en|女性電影水晶+露西獎|Women in Film Crystal + Lucy Awards|女性電影水晶獎}}。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbiz411.com/2012/06/14/meryl-streep-viola-davis-love-fest-at-women-in-film-awards|title=Meryl Streep-Viola Davis Love Fest at Women in Film Awards|work=showbiz|date=2012-06-14|accessdate=2012-07-08|archive-date=2012-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120618041901/http://www.showbiz411.com/2012/06/14/meryl-streep-viola-davis-love-fest-at-women-in-film-awards|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 6月25日，好萊塢星光大道委員商會宣布戴維斯為娛樂專業人士新組的一員，而戴維斯也將名留[[好萊塢星光大道|好萊塢星光大道]]。<ref>{{cite web|last=Gans|first=Andrew|url=http://www.playbill.com/article/viola-davis-helen-mirren-jane-lynch-olympia-dukakis-jennifer-hudson-are-hollywood-walk-of-fame-recipients-com-195038|title=Viola Davis, Helen Mirren, Jane Lynch, Olympia Dukakis, Jennifer Hudson Are Hollywood Walk of Fame Recipients|date=2012-06-25|accessdate=2012-07-08}}</ref>

