2014年2月，戴維斯加入了由[[彼得·諾沃克|彼得·諾沃克]]開創、[[珊達·萊梅斯|珊達·萊梅斯]]擔任執行製作並由{{link-en|ShondaLand|ShondaLand}}製作的《[[逍遙法外_(電視劇)|逍遙法外]]》[[逍遙法外_(第一季)#ep1|試播集]]演出，並擔任女主角。<ref>{{cite web|title=Viola Davis to Star in ABC Drama 'How to Get Away With Murder'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/viola-davis-star-abc-drama-680273|publisher=hollywood reporter|accessdate=2014-05-10|archive-date=2014-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140521142041/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/viola-davis-star-abc-drama-680273|dead-url=no}}</ref> 該劇在2014年5月8日獲得[[美國廣播公司|ABC]]預訂，<ref>{{cite web|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/05/abc-picks-up-shonda-rhimes-how-to-get-away-with-murder-anthony-anderson-american-crime/|title=ABC New Series Pickups: 'Selfie', 'Forever', Galavant', 'Whispers', 'How To Get Away With Murder', 'American Crime', 'Black-ish', Jeff Lowell Comedy|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2014-05-08|accessdate=2014-05-12|archive-date=2014-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713050410/http://www.deadline.com/2014/05/abc-picks-up-shonda-rhimes-how-to-get-away-with-murder-anthony-anderson-american-crime/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Cynthia Littleton|url=http://variety.com/2014/tv/news/abc-orders-viola-davis-drama-how-to-get-away-with-murder-1201176035/|title=ABC Orders ‘Marvel’s Agent Carter,’ 4 Other Dramas and 4 Comedies|publisher=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝雜誌]]|date=2014-05-08|accessdate=2014-05-05|archive-date=2015-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150831120708/http://variety.com/2014/tv/news/abc-orders-viola-davis-drama-how-to-get-away-with-murder-1201176035/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 並於2014年9月25日開播。<ref name="premiere">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/abc-sets-fall-premiere-dates-718576|title=ABC Sets Fall Premiere Dates|publisher=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]|date=2014-07-15|accessdate=2014-07-16|author=Philiana Ng|archive-date=2015-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150302151307/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/abc-sets-fall-premiere-dates-718576|dead-url=no}}</ref> 該劇首播後，戴維斯的演技受到了電視評論家的一致讚賞，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/la-et-st-how-to-get-away-with-murder-review-20140925-column.html|title='How to Get Away With Murder' keeps spotlight on Viola Davis|publisher=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|accessdate=2016|archive-date=2017-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171214025435/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/la-et-st-how-to-get-away-with-murder-review-20140925-column.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2014/10/15/how-get-away-murder|title=How to Get Away With Murder|publisher=[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]|accessdate=2016|archive-date=2016-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161219202422/http://www.ew.com/article/2014/10/15/how-get-away-murder|dead-url=no}}</ref> 而戴維斯更在隔年的[[第67屆黃金時段艾美獎|第67屆黃金時段艾美獎]]上獲得{{le|黃金時段艾美獎最佳劇情類影集女主角|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Lead Actress in a Drama Series|最佳劇情類影集女主角獎}}，成為首位奪得該獎項的非裔女性。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Nakamura|first1=Reid|title=Viola Davis and Taraji P. Henson Make Emmy History With ‘How to Get Away With Murder,’ ‘Empire’ Roles|url=https://www.google.ca/webhp?sourceid=chrome-instant&ion=1&espv=2&ie=UTF-8#q=viola%20davis%20emmy%20nomination|accessdate=2015-08-27|archive-date=2019-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190531214316/https://www.google.ca/webhp?sourceid=chrome-instant&ion=1&espv=2&ie=UTF-8#q=viola%20davis%20emmy%20nomination|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Rachel Handler. [http://time.com/4048253/viola-davis-emmys-speech-ellen/ "Watch Viola Davis Explain Her Historic Emmys Speech to Ellen DeGeneres"] {{Wayback|url=http://time.com/4048253/viola-davis-emmys-speech-ellen/ |date=20150928084905 }}. 時代雜誌, September 24, 2015. Retrieved September 28, 2015</ref><ref>Michael Gold. [http://www.nytimes.com/live/emmys-2015/viola-daviss-emotional-emmys-acceptance-speech/ Viola Davis’s Emmy Speech]. Awards Season. The 2015 Emmy Awards. [[紐約時報|紐約時報]], September 20, 2015. Retrieved September 28, 2015.</ref><ref>Stephanie Merry, [https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/style-blog/wp/2015/09/20/2015-emmy-awards-complete-live-coverage/ "Emmy Awards: ‘Game of Thrones’ beats ‘Mad Men’, Viola Davis becomes first African American to win best actress in drama, Jon Hamm finally wins best actor, ‘Veep’ sweeps"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/style-blog/wp/2015/09/20/2015-emmy-awards-complete-live-coverage/ |date=20150928173228 }}, [[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]], September 20, 2015. Retrieved September 28, 2015.</ref> 戴維斯亦連續兩年憑藉該劇奪得[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]劇情類影集最佳女演員獎，後續又入圍了三次黃金時段艾美獎。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/15/arts/television/emmy-nominations-2016-will-game-of-thrones-rule-again.html?_r=0|work=New York Times |title=Emmy Nominations 2016: Game of Thrones Rules Again |date=2016-07-07|accessdate=2016-07-20}}</ref>

2016年，戴維斯加入了改編自[[DC漫畫|DC]][[自殺小隊|同名漫畫]]的[[超級英雄電影|超級英雄電影]]《[[自殺突擊隊_(電影)|自殺突擊隊]]》，並飾演政府官員[[阿曼達·沃勒|阿曼達·華勒]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latino-review.com/news/exclusive-viola-davis-bags-amanda-waller-role-in-suicide-squad|title=EXCLUSIVE: Viola Davis Bags Amanda Waller Role In 'Suicide Squad'|date=2014-12-16|work=Latino-Review.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217080509/http://www.latino-review.com/news/exclusive-viola-davis-bags-amanda-waller-role-in-suicide-squad|archivedate=2014-12-17}}</ref> 同年，戴維斯於主演之電視劇《逍遙法外》開始擔任製作人一職。

2017年1月5日，戴維斯正式名留好萊塢星光大道，並由好友梅麗·史翠普頒獎予她，而《逍遙法外》主創彼得·諾沃克、製作人{{link-en|比爾·德埃利亞|Bill D'Elia}}及演員[[查理·韋伯|查理·韋伯]]、[[比利·布朗|比利·布朗]]、[[艾爾佛瑞德·伊睿克|艾爾佛瑞德·伊睿克]]與[[柯納德·里嘉摩拉|康拉德·里卡摩拉]]和《藩籬》演員{{link-en|喬凡·阿戴波|Jovan Adepo}}、{{link-en|史蒂芬·亨德森|Stephen Henderson (actor)|史蒂芬·麥金利·亨德森}}、{{link-en|莎奈雅·席德尼|Saniyya Sidney}}、[[麥凱泰·威廉遜|麥凱泰·威廉遜]]等人皆到場祝賀共襄盛舉。<ref name="Walk of Fame">{{cite news|url=http://variety.com/2017/film/awards/walk-of-fame-honoree-viola-davis-1201952550/|title=Walk of Fame Honoree Viola Davis Reveals Her ‘Big A-Ha Moment’ in Hollywood|work=綜藝雜誌|date=2017-01-05|accessdate=2017-01-06}}</ref> 同年，戴維斯二度被〈時代雜誌〉評選為「時代百大人物」之一。<ref name="The 100 2017"/>

戴維斯於電影版《[[藩籬_(電影)|藩籬]]》中繼續飾演蘿絲·麥斯森，並因該劇獲得影評人讚賞，同時榮獲許多影評人獎項，更在該頒獎季（2016年–2017年）中榮獲其生涯首座奧斯卡金像獎、英國電影學院獎、金球獎以及第5座美國演員工會獎。該次為她第三度入圍奧斯卡金像獎，創下奧斯卡史上獲最多次提名的非裔女演員，<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/arts-and-entertainment/wp/2017/01/24/viola-daviss-historic-oscar-nod-could-lead-to-a-win-and-another-great-speech/?utm_term=.6e4c5bf30a58|title=Viola Davis makes history with her third Oscar nod. We might be in for an epic speech|author=Bethonie Butler|work=華盛頓郵報|date=2017-01-24|accessdate=2017-01-27}}</ref> 亦是首位同時獲得奧斯卡、艾美獎及東尼獎演技獎項殊榮的非裔演員，躋身[[表演奖大满贯|演技三冠王]]。<ref>{{cite web|author=Mic |url=https://mic.com/articles/166030/oscars-2017-viola-davis-first-black-actress-3-oscar-nominations#.jk2CfR5FC |title=Oscars 2017: Viola Davis just became the first black actress to earn 3 Oscar nominations |publisher=Mic |date= |accessdate=2017-01-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Maxwell Strachan|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/viola-davis-triple-crown_us_58b05b5de4b060480e073ce7|title=Viola Davis Just Became The First Black Woman To Win An Oscar, Emmy And Tony For Acting|publisher=[[赫芬頓郵報|赫芬頓郵報]]|date=2017-02-26|accessdate=2017-02-26|archive-date=2017-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170227045714/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/viola-davis-triple-crown_us_58b05b5de4b060480e073ce7|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Lisa Ryan |url=http://nymag.com/thecut/2017/02/viola-davis-first-black-actor-to-win-oscar-emmy-and-tony.html |title=Viola Davis, First Black Actor to Win Oscar, Emmy, and Tony |publisher=Nymag.com |date= |accessdate=2017-02-27 |archive-date=2017-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170228083503/http://nymag.com/thecut/2017/02/viola-davis-first-black-actor-to-win-oscar-emmy-and-tony.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2018年主演由[[史蒂夫·麥奎因_(導演)|史提夫·麥昆]]執導的電影《[[寡婦_(電影)|寡婦]]》，演技獲得諸多認可，並第二度獲英國電影學院獎提名最佳女主角。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2019/jan/09/the-full-list-of-nominations-for-the-baftas-2019|title=The full list of nominations for the Baftas 2019|publisher=[[衛報|衛報]]|date=2019-01-09|accessdate=2021-03-17|archive-date=2019-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190109114504/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2019/jan/09/the-full-list-of-nominations-for-the-baftas-2019|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年和[[查德維克·博斯曼|查德維克·博斯曼]]繼《{{link-en|激樂人心|Get on Up (film)}}》後，再度合作演出改編樂壇偉人的電影，共同主演[[Netflix|Netflix]][[Netflix原創節目列表#電影|原創電影]]《[[藍調天后|藍調天后]]》，飾演美國已逝[[藍調|藍調]]女歌手{{le|瑪·雷尼|Ma Rainey}}，演技收獲廣泛好評。憑此獲得生涯第六座美國演員工會獎<ref name="27thSAG" /><ref name="27thSAGDeadline" />，成為首位獲得兩座美國演員工會電影女主角獎的非裔女演員<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2021-04-05/sag-awards-2021-viola-davis-chadwick-boseman-winners|title=Viola Davis and Chadwick Boseman were part of historic wins at 2021 SAG Awards|publisher=洛杉磯時報|author=Christi Carras|date=2021-04-05|accessdate=2021-04-08|archive-date=2021-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210405175812/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2021-04-05/sag-awards-2021-viola-davis-chadwick-boseman-winners|dead-url=no}}</ref>，亦獲[[哥譚獨立電影獎|哥譚獨立電影獎]]女演員貢獻獎肯定<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ifp.org/press/nominations-announced-for-30th-ifp-gotham-awards/|title=Nominations Announced for 30th IFP Gotham Awards|author=Zach Mandinach|publisher={{le|獨立電影製作人計畫|Independent Filmmaker Project}}|date=2020-11-12|accessdate=2020-12-20|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208153602/https://www.ifp.org/press/nominations-announced-for-30th-ifp-gotham-awards/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://thegotham.org/press/30th-annual-ifp-gotham-awards-winners-announced/|title=30th Annual IFP Gotham Awards Winners Announced|author=Zach Mandinach|publisher=獨立電影製作人計畫|date=2021-01-11|accessdate=2021-03-14|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114195330/https://thegotham.org/press/30th-annual-ifp-gotham-awards-winners-announced/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2021/01/gotham-awards-full-winners-list-live-gotham-film-and-media-institute-1234671454/|title=Gotham Awards Full Winners List: 'Nomadland', 'The Forty-Year-Old Version', 'I May Destroy You', Riz Ahmed, Nicole Beharie Among Honorees|publisher=Deadline Hollywood|author=Dino-Ray Ramos|date=2021-01-11|accessdate=2021-01-12|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112032811/https://deadline.com/2021/01/gotham-awards-full-winners-list-live-gotham-film-and-media-institute-1234671454/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並第四度入圍奧斯卡金像獎，打破自身與[[奧克塔維亞·斯賓塞|奧塔薇亞·史班森]]皆入圍三次的紀錄，成為奧斯卡史上獲得最多次提名的非裔女演員<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ew.com/awards/oscars/viola-davis-most-nominated-black-actress-oscar-nominations/|title=Viola Davis makes Oscars history as the most-nominated Black actress ever|publisher=[[娛樂週刊|娛樂週刊]]|author=Joey Nolfi|date=2021-03-15|accessdate=2021-03-17|archive-date=2021-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315124045/https://ew.com/awards/oscars/viola-davis-most-nominated-black-actress-oscar-nominations/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2021-03-15/oscars-2021-viola-davis-black-actress-most-nominations-in-oscar-history|title=Viola Davis is now the most nominated Black actress in Oscars history|publisher=洛杉磯時報|author=Christie D'Zurilla|date=2021-03-15|accessdate=2021-03-17|archive-date=2021-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317153634/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2021-03-15/oscars-2021-viola-davis-black-actress-most-nominations-in-oscar-history|dead-url=no}}</ref>，另入圍金球獎<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.goldenglobes.com/winners-nominees/2021|title=Winners & Nominees 2021|publisher=[[金球獎|金球獎]]|date=2021-03-01|accessdate=2021-03-01|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301042943/https://www.goldenglobes.com/winners-nominees/2021|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2021/02/2021-golden-globes-winners-list-1234702653/|title=Golden Globes: ‘Nomadland’ Wins Best Motion Picture Drama – The Complete Winners List|publisher=Deadline Hollywood|author=Erik Pedersen|date=2021-02-28|accessdate=2021-03-01|archive-date=2021-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301044443/https://deadline.com/2021/02/2021-golden-globes-winners-list-1234702653/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[澳大利亞影視藝術學院獎|澳洲影視藝術學院國際獎]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.aacta.org/our-news/media-room/australian-academy-announces-winners-for-the-10th-aacta-international-awards/|title=Australian Academy announces winners for the 10th AACTA International Awards|publisher={{le|澳洲影視藝術學院|Australian Academy of Cinema and Television Arts}}|date=2021-03-06|accessdate=2021-03-06|archive-date=2021-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306013127/https://www.aacta.org/our-news/media-room/australian-academy-announces-winners-for-the-10th-aacta-international-awards/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[評論家選擇電影獎|評論家選擇電影獎]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://criticschoice.com/2021/02/film-nominations-announced-for-the-26th-annual-critics-choice-awards/|title=Film nominees for the 26th annual Critics Choice Awards have been announced|publisher=[[評論家選擇協會|評論家選擇協會]]|date=2021-02-08|accessdate=2021-02-08|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208175411/https://criticschoice.com/2021/02/film-nominations-announced-for-the-26th-annual-critics-choice-awards/|dead-url=no}}</ref>與[[獨立精神獎|獨立精神獎]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.filmindependent.org/blog/2021-film-independent-spirit-award-nominations-announced/|title=2021 Film Independent Spirit Award Nominations Announced!|publisher=獨立電影（Film Independent）|author=Matt Warren|date=2021-01-26|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126162015/https://www.filmindependent.org/blog/2021-film-independent-spirit-award-nominations-announced/|dead-url=no}}</ref>等。

